---
import MainLayout from "../layout/MainLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "M Durrani | Home"
---

<MainLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
		<div class="container">
			<main>
				<section class="hero-section">
					<div class="glass-panel">
						<h1 class="animated-title">Mohammad Durrani</h1>
						<div class="title-underline"></div>
						<div class="hero-content">
							<p class="intro-text">Hey. I'm Mohammad, a <span class="highlight">Full-Stack Web Developer</span> and <span class="highlight">Writer</span> from Pakistan. Currently, I'm working on <a href="https://proudlypakistani.com">ProudlyPakistani</a> and <a href="https://amplifywow.com">AmplifyWoW</a>. The primary function of this space is to consolidate my works. Beyond that, I hope it provides insight not only into the problems and conceptual areas that interest me, but also into the core principles that guide my work.</p>
							<p>I welcome opportunities for collaboration, be it on current or new projects. If any of our interests align, please reach out!</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
				
				<section class="values-section">
					<div class="glass-panel">
						<h2>Values <span class="section-accent"></span></h2>
						<div class="content-grid">
							<div class="value-item">
								<span class="value-number">01</span>
								<p>The projects I work on should be <span class="emphasis">ethical</span> and contribute positively to society. I evaluate potential work through this lens first and foremost.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="value-item">
								<span class="value-number">02</span>
								<p><span class="emphasis">Accessibility standards</span> must be met in all my work. Digital experiences should be inclusive and usable by everyone, regardless of ability.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="value-item">
								<span class="value-number">03</span>
								<p><span class="emphasis">No dark patterns</span> - I refuse to implement design tricks that manipulate users or compromise their agency. User interfaces should be honest and transparent.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="value-item">
								<span class="value-number">04</span>
								<p><span class="emphasis">Write honestly</span> - Whether code or prose, clarity and honesty are fundamental. Complexity should be made accessible, not obscured.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="value-item">
								<span class="value-number">05</span>
								<p>Software should prioritize <span class="emphasis">performance</span>, thoughtful <span class="emphasis">UX design</span>, <span class="emphasis">security</span>, <span class="emphasis">privacy</span>, and <span class="emphasis">data-driven decision making</span> - no assumptions.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="interests-section">
					<div class="glass-panel">
						<h2>Interests <span class="section-accent"></span></h2>
						<div class="interests-grid">
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="software">
								<h3>Respectful Software</h3>
								<p>I'm passionate about creating software that is performant, secure, and reliable. Software that respects its users through clear interfaces and accessible design.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="opensource">
								<h3>Open Source</h3>
								<p>I believe in the power of open source software to democratize technology and foster collaborative innovation across borders and communities.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="writing">
								<h3>Writing Well</h3>
								<p>Clear, honest, and impactful writing is an art form I continually pursue, whether in documentation, essays, or creative work.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="development">
								<h3>Developing Nations</h3>
								<p>I'm focused on potential solutions for challenges facing developing countries, particularly in Pakistan and South Asia. Many developing regions share similar obstacles, and collaborative problem-solving could yield powerful results.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="southasia">
								<h3>United South Asia</h3>
								<p>I envision and work toward a stable, united South Asia where cooperation transcends historical divisions and creates prosperity for all.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="environment">
								<h3>Environmental Health</h3>
								<p>Clean air is a massive problem in South Asia. I'm interested in technological and policy solutions that address environmental challenges affecting millions of people.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="interest-card" data-interest="education">
								<h3>Modern Education</h3>
								<p>I care deeply about developing a new, modern curriculum that equips young people with the mindset and knowledge needed for effective problem-solving and lifelong learning.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</MainLayout>